OL,3,CDisabled Motability scheme users face
OL,4,Cnew charges after government tax hikes
OL,6,FDisabled people using the Motability
OL,7,Fcar leasing scheme are set to face
OL,8,Fhigher costs as the organisation seeks
OL,9,Fto offset #300 million in new taxes
OL,10,Fintroduced in last year's autumn
OL,11,Fbudget.
OL,13,FChanges include revised mileage
OL,14,Fallowances, new charges for taking
OL,15,Fvehicles abroad, and advance payment
OL,16,Fincreases of up to #400 for new leases
OL,17,Fstarting after July 1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
