OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774699371
OL,3,CDisabled Motability scheme users face
OL,4,Cnew charges after government tax hikes
OL,6,FIt comes amid a backdrop of fierce
OL,7,Fpolitical scrutiny towards the scheme,
OL,8,Fwith the Conservative leader Kemi
OL,9,FBadenoch using her speech at last
OL,10,Fyear's party conference to promise far
OL,11,Ftighter restrictions for those with
OL,12,Fall but the most "severe physical
OL,13,Fmobility needs".
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,20,FWhat is the Motability Scheme?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
