CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774699371
OL,3,CDisabled Motability scheme users face
OL,4,Cnew charges after government tax hikes
OL,6,FThe Motability scheme allows people
OL,7,Freceiving certain disability benefits
OL,8,Fto direct some or all of their
OL,9,Fpayments toward leasing a new car or
OL,10,Faccessible vehicle.
OL,12,FEligibility is restricted to those
OL,13,Fentitled to the higher or enhanced
OL,14,Frate of the mobility component of
OL,15,Fdisability benefit, and the scheme is
OL,16,Fcurrently used by around 890,000
OL,17,Fpeople across the UK.
OL,19,FLast month, Reform UK said it planned
OL,20,Fto make sweeping changes to Motability
OL,21,Fto "end the abuse" of the scheme.
OL,26,@}D@DOU}D@RO]
