CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774699371
OL,3,CDisabled Motability scheme users face
OL,4,Cnew charges after government tax hikes
OL,6,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,7,Fechoed this sentiment at her party's
OL,8,Fconference in Manchester last year as
OL,9,Fwell, calling for tougher eligibility
OL,10,Fcriteria.
OL,12,FWhat's causing the higher costs?
OL,14,FThe changes come from decisions made
OL,15,FReeves' autumn budget.
OL,17,FThe government announced it would
OL,18,Fintroduce VAT on advance payments for
OL,19,Fthe scheme and apply insurance premium
OL,20,Ftax to leases from July 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
