OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774699371
OL,3,CDisabled Motability scheme users face
OL,4,Cnew charges after government tax hikes
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves also
OL,7,Fannounced that the scheme would no
OL,8,Flonger use "luxury cars" such as BMW
OL,9,Fand Mercedes-Benz vehicles.
OL,11,FMotability says these combined
OL,12,Fmeasures will cost the business #300
OL,13,Fmillion in additional taxes.
OL,15,FWhat changes will users of the scheme
OL,16,Fsee?
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
