PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774699371
OL,3,CDisabled Motability scheme users face
OL,4,Cnew charges after government tax hikes
OL,6,FOn Thursday, chief executive of
OL,7,FMotability Operations, Andrew Miller,
OL,8,Ftold people on the scheme that it will
OL,9,Fintroduce changes to deal with the
OL,10,Fcost.
OL,12,F"Together, these tax changes mean it
OL,13,Fwill cost significantly more to run
OL,14,Fthe scheme," he said in a letter.
OL,16,F"If we did nothing, the average cost
OL,17,Fof a new lease would increase by
OL,18,Faround #1,100. It was clear to me that
OL,19,Fsimply passing all these costs on to
OL,20,Fcustomers was not an option.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@LO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774699371
OL,3,CDisabled Motability scheme users face
OL,4,Cnew charges after government tax hikes
OL,6,F"We had to carefully consider how to
OL,7,Freduce the tax impact as much as
OL,8,Fpossible but also, focusing on changes
OL,9,Fthat reflect how most customers
OL,10,Falready use their vehicles."
OL,12,FHe outlined plans to reduce the annual
OL,13,Fmileage allowances, increase excess
OL,14,Fmileage fees, change tyre replacement
OL,15,Flimits and introduce a charge for
OL,16,Ftaking cars abroad.
OL,18,FIt is understood that customers taking
OL,19,Fnew leases after July 1 will see an
OL,20,Faverage increase to advance payments
OL,21,Fof between #300 and #400.
